descriptionHTML:
NIGHTTMM is a designer watchface app for Android Wear devices. White dot points at the minutes, bite made by the hour. App has a nine colors customization and works in ambient mode. Have a great TTMM.

Compatible ONLY with devices with round screen like: Huawei Watch, Motorola Moto 360, LG Watch R

Idea & design : Albert Salamon
Android programming : Artur Salamon
